<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Probably a bit too late for Brian, but in case anyone else is wondering the same thing, I fit Brian&apos;s profile. I generally prefer &apos;literature&apos;. eg, Bo<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Probably a bit too late for Brian, but in case anyone else is wondering the same thing, I fit Brian's profile. I generally prefer 'literature'. eg, Booker books<br /><br />I've only read Eye of the Needle. I'd say it is a well-told thriller. Enjoyable, but not demanding to read. Comparable to, say, Dan Brown, Lee Child, Harlan Corben.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
