<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1616556-can-someone-remind-me---why-when-the">Can someone remind me --why, when the Needle had discovered the secret--why couldn&#39;t he just find a way to radio the information back to Germany? I suspect it was because German spy networks did not have radio support from the Fatherland. Is that correct? British (and French Underground) operatives had those transmitters/receivers disguised as suitcases; but German agents did not benefit from such infrastructure, yes?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
