<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/11335584-jerry-davis"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11335584-jerry-davis">Jerry Davis</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">He had a radio, but didn&apos;t trust the operatives on the receiving end with accurately relaying his information. This was mentioned after he took the pi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">He had a radio, but didn't trust the operatives on the receiving end with accurately relaying his information. This was mentioned after he took the pictures, escaped and reached a town. He felt he made the right decision after the pictures he sent to the Portugal embassy were turned over to British intelligence.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
