<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23476412-edge-of-eternity"><img alt="Edge of Eternity: by Ken Follett (The Century Trilogy, Book 3) | Summary &amp; Analysis" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1414624998l/23476412._SX98_.jpg" />
